description: Whether they're on the road, working out or relaxing on the couch, your users want complete control of their music. With this agent users can search, pause, skip or shuffle in your app, just by asking.
shortDescription: Play and control your music and playlists
examples:
User: Switch to workout music.
User: Put on my late night playlist.
User: Can you please play a song from my favorite playlist?
User: Play a song from Spotify.
User: I want to listen to some music.
User: Play an album by Madonna.
User: Play something by The Rolling Stones.
